    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i can call someone but they'll just tell me the same things. \"hang in there\" or \"it'll get better.\" but it won't. the doctors won't fix it. there is no relief coming. sometimes i just sit here thinking that the only real way to actually find some peace is to just... stop. like, why is it considered so wrong to just want the noise to stop?",
